-- Repsol May Sign Romanian Partnership This Week, Hotnews.ro Says
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-02-20T11:39:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-20/repsol-may-sign-romanian-partnership-this-week-hotnews-ro-says.html
Repsol SA , Spain’s largest oil
producer, may sign a partnership deal with an unidentified
Romanian company by the end of the week to carry out oil and gas
operations in the country, Hotnews.ro  reported today , citing
unnamed government officials from the eastern European nation.  Kristian Rix , a Repsol spokesman, declined to comment when
contacted by Bloomberg.  Andrei Zaharescu , a Romanian government
spokesman, didn’t immediately respond to a Bloomberg query.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Irina Savu  in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  